rows.label: qst700804_msg0002
rows.name:
Curses...! My brothers, I
am sorry, mo! Step over my
corpse and go on, mo!

rows.label: qst700804_msg0101
rows.name: Fufu, you know some difficult words.

rows.label: qst700804_msg0102
rows.name:
But if you don't apologize properly
when you should, it's not cool!

rows.label: qst700804_msg0202
rows.name:
Then, with that strong resolve
in your heart, go and apologize
to the old woman next!

rows.label: qst700804_msg0301
rows.name:
Hmm, I can't say I'm impressed by
you wagering your life so easily.

rows.label: qst700804_msg0302
rows.name:
Come now, that old woman
is waiting for you.

rows.label: qst700804_msg0401
rows.name:
Are you done? Then, I'll have
you go to Oulu-san's place.

rows.label: qst700804_msg0501
rows.name:
My, my, talking about corpses
is out of the question.

rows.label: qst700804_msg0502
rows.name:
If you apologize honestly, that old
woman will surely forgive you.

rows.label: qst700804_msg0601
rows.name:
All right, all right.
Corpse or whatever, just
go and apologize already.

rows.label: qst700804_msg0602
rows.name:
That old granny is
surely waiting for you.

rows.label: qst700804_msg0701
rows.name:
Rest assured. I have no
intention of taking your life.

rows.label: qst700804_msg0702
rows.name: Now, go to that old woman.

rows.label: qst700804_msg0801
rows.name:
Honestly, where did you
learn such words...

rows.label: qst700804_msg0802
rows.name: Hurry up and apologize to that lady.

rows.label: qst700804_msg0901
rows.name:
I see. So you're the one
playing the eldest brother.

rows.label: qst700804_msg0902
rows.name:
If that's the case, then all the more
reason for you to take the lead and
apologize to that lady, don't you think?
